dmca.title: Reseller Threatened
dmca.body:
It is urgent that you remove the following item from your web-site - "Wet Seal Skirts" Seller ID 16339.

We need a letter from you claiming we did not sell you this merchandise or give you permission to use the "Wet Seal Label" or Name.

If this item is not removed from your web-site, you will be hearing from the Attorneys at Wet Seal and also Mimi Chica division of Promises, Promises, Inc..

Thank you,
